Terri Conn https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Terri_Conn 0 Terri Conn (born January 28, 1975), formerly known as Terri Colombino, is an American actress. She is known for her roles as Katie Peretti on As the World Turns and as Christine “Aubrey Wentworth" Karr on One Life to Live. On July 1, 2011, she married her former As the World Turns co-star, Austin Peck. Terri_Conn ( born January_28_,_1975 ) , formerly_known as Terri_Colombino , is an_American_actress .
